    "name": "Twilight Ferry",
    "steam_appid": 3141870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Twilight Ferry is an adventure game inspired by the old epics of Finnic mythology.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Every lost soul needs a guide.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Someone is waiting—someone only <strong>You</strong> can save.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>If they forgot their past, forgot your face, forgot every moment you shared—</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Would you still stay?</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tuoni—God of Death—plans to wipe out humanity from the face of the earth. Tytti, an emotionally limited Ferrymaiden, possesses the power to stop him but needs help to discover it. You see Tytti lose all her memories due to a curse by Tuoni. Her journey would be over, if <strong>You</strong> had not been there...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/7472b08c9766f5df5d4a35d687384c9d.poster.avif?t=1767978604\" width=1170 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/7472b08c9766f5df5d4a35d687384c9d.webm?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/7472b08c9766f5df5d4a35d687384c9d.mp4?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Tytti to master human emotions, navigate the underworld's challenges, and ultimately confront Tuoni. As you help her to recover her lost memories, Tytti grows more capable and courageous, gaining strength to overcome the obstacles in her path and restore balance in the cycle of rebirth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the creatures and personalities along the river that separates the underworld from the material realm. Shamans, spirits… and Mushroomfolk? Traverse hidden grottos in search of answers, and to free souls of the deceased who are stuck in limbo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/c68cce12671b29035e9e2fca046c0ec2.poster.avif?t=1767978604\" width=1170 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/c68cce12671b29035e9e2fca046c0ec2.webm?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/c68cce12671b29035e9e2fca046c0ec2.mp4?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Emotion Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Tytti focus by changing her emotions through <i>Meditation</i>. Each emotion offers different dialogue options and abilities to traverse the world. Be wary of Tytti’s mood—it can make her act impulsively if left unchecked! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/c959615c658cc6e945ca79e8f5d6f4b5.poster.avif?t=1767978604\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/c959615c658cc6e945ca79e8f5d6f4b5.webm?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/c959615c658cc6e945ca79e8f5d6f4b5.mp4?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overcome Challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you’ll confront not only external enemies but also the depths of Tytti’s own emotional struggles. Manage Tytti's emotions correctly to solve puzzles and beat adversaries in the ancient rite of<i> Spellsinging</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/ad3d1d1aa6bc120b95d4bc90e8b101c3.poster.avif?t=1767978604\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/ad3d1d1aa6bc120b95d4bc90e8b101c3.webm?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141870/extras/ad3d1d1aa6bc120b95d4bc90e8b101c3.mp4?t=1767978604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A tranquil audiovisual experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience an unique visual style combining 2D pixel art with a fully lit 3D environment, together with a &quot;beautifully eerie&quot; soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
